OL,3,CSynthetic opioid deaths almost
OL,4,Cquadruple in England and Wales
OL,6,FNitazenes are powerful synthetic
OL,7,Fopioids, man-made drugs that act on
OL,8,Fthe same brain receptors as natural
OL,9,Fopioids from the opium poppy.
OL,11,FThey are usually sold as a white or
OL,12,Fyellow-brown powder, or in crystalline
OL,13,Fform, and have also been found mixed
OL,14,Fwith heroin, ketamine, and synthetic
OL,15,Fcannabinoids.
OL,17,FSome nitazenes are very potent,
OL,18,Fpotentially up to 500 times stronger
OL,19,Fthan heroin, and are increasingly
OL,20,Ffound in counterfeit prescription
OL,21,Fmedicine.
