OL,3,CSynthetic opioid deaths almost
OL,4,Cquadruple in England and Wales
OL,6,FMeanwhile, drug poisoning deaths in
OL,7,FEngland and Wales have hit a record
OL,8,Fhigh, with 5,565 fatalities registered
OL,9,Flast year, a 2.1% rise on 2023, double
OL,10,Fthe number recorded in 2012.
OL,12,FThis marks the fourteenth consecutive
OL,13,Fannual increase.
OL,15,FThe ONS has warned that figures for
OL,16,Fdrug misuse and specific substances
OL,17,Fare likely undercounts, as around a
OL,18,Ffifth of death registrations do not
OL,19,Frecord which drugs were involved.
