OL,6,FIt also noted that due to reporting
OL,7,Fdelays, roughly half of the deaths
OL,8,Fregistered in 2024 occurred in
OL,9,Fprevious years.
OL,11,FResearch from King's College London
OL,12,Fsuggests the true scale of the crisis
OL,13,Fmay be far worse, estimating that
OL,14,Fopioid deaths between 2011 and 2022
OL,15,Fwere 55% higher than official figures.
