OL,6,FThe Turning Point charity, which helps
OL,7,Fpeople with substance abuse problems,
OL,8,Fcalled for increased availability of
OL,9,Fmedication to be given in the event of
OL,10,Fopioid overdoses.
OL,12,FChief operating officer Clare Taylor
OL,13,Fsaid: "Lab-produced opioids pose a
OL,14,Fsignificant risk to life due to their
OL,15,Fpotency and this is reflected in the
OL,16,Ffact that deaths related to nitazenes
OL,17,Fhave increased four-fold compared to
OL,18,Fthe previous year.
