OL,6,FThe ONS said cocaine has remained the
OL,7,Fsecond-most used drug after cannabis
OL,8,Fin England and Wales over the past
OL,9,Fdecade.
OL,11,FMore than three-quarters of cocaine-
OL,12,Flinked deaths in 2024 were among men,
OL,13,Fwith 982 male deaths compared with 297
OL,14,Ffemale.
