OL,6,FChief Executive Mark Moody told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "Drug use doesn't happen in
OL,8,Fisolation. It's linked to housing
OL,9,Finstability, poverty, poor mental
OL,10,Fhealth, and an overwhelmed justice
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,F"Tackling these broader issues will
OL,14,Ftake time, but without urgent action
OL,15,Fnow, drug-related deaths will continue
OL,16,Fon the same trajectory, with more
OL,17,Flives lost, more families shattered,
OL,18,Fand more communities left behind."
